Package: chronicle
Type: Package
Title: Grammar for creating Rmarkdown reports 
Version: 0.0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Philippe", "Heymans Smith", email = "pheymanss@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: <pheymanss@gmail.com>
Description: Inspired on keras' interface to add layers to a neural network,
    chronicle provides an interface to create an Rmarkdown report by adding 
    modules like plots and tables to a base. 
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0),
    data.table,
    magrittr
